      <t>This document specifies TRILL OAM Fault Management. Methods in this document follow the IEEE 802.1 CFM framework and reuse OAM tools where possible. Additional messages and TLVs are defined for TRILL specific applications or where a different set of information is required other than IEEE 802.1 CFM.</t>
